Atomic Operation ---->  Effect

atomic_set(&counter,5) ----> counter = 5
atomic_add(&counter,5) ----> counter = counter+5
atomic_sub(&counter,5) ----> counter = counter-5
atomic_inc(&counter,5) ----> counter = counter+1




Screen Lock:

SMP Machine : Multiprocessor:
single memonry


Semaphore :


Single Processor ----> Multiple Processor
Disable Kernel Preemption ----> Aquire spin lock
Enable Kernel Preemption ----> Release spin lock



POSIX Thread :


pthread_join(thread1,NULL)
pthread_join(thread2,NULL)

